http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-wAJo6GQg3D4/U4vf9IPYJSI/AAAAAAAAGRo/ROjteLYhcLc/s1600/Carp+State+Records.jpg
3: Use coordinated small multiples
http://projects.flowingdata.com/timeuse/
4: Feel free to show uncertainty
http://cl.ly/image/0u162K3y3T2r
5: Feel free to make inventive choices
http://cl.ly/image/0g3v3J3p0n0N

